snippet.title: A Juggler's Tale - Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Lead Abby the string puppet through a bruised, but beautiful fairy tale world in this cinematic adventure. Coming for PC, PlayStation 4/5, Xbox and Nintendo Switch on September 29, 2021!

✨ http://wishlist.ajugglerstale.com ✨

Solve riddles, evade traps and shake off pursuers on the way to find freedom. Can Abby take control of her fate with all the strings attached?


#ajugglerstale #indiegame
